userinterface.graph

Class AxisSettings

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • userinterface.graph.AxisSettings
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable, SettingOwner

    public class AxisSettings
extends java.util.Observable
implements SettingOwner
    Representation of an axis of a Graph. The settings are propagated to the JFreeChart library.
